&lt;h3&gt;Are you a skilled Board Certified Behavior Analyst (BCBA) who is passionate about empowering fellow Clinical Leaders?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re a natural mentor that thrives when disseminating clinical knowledge, and inspiring clinical excellence in new &amp;amp; future BCBAs, this is the perfect role for you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Commitment to Children&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Centria, we believe in making a lasting positive impact. We offer top-quality, compassionate ABA therapy through child-led engagement and fun learning experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will be integral in ensuring our individualized programs and treatment plans are developed and delivered with the highest standards of care by training, mentoring, and supporting Clinical Apprentices, Behavior Consultant Trainees, and new Supervising Clinicians.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation and Incentives:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1. Base salary up to&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;$105,000 &lt;/strong&gt;(based on experience).&lt;br&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;Signing bonus.&lt;br&gt;3. Monthly and weekly&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;bonus structure averaging&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;$1,000 or more&amp;nbsp;per month&lt;/strong&gt;!&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Let&#39;s Talk! We know that outstanding clinical quality is invaluable, and we are ready to compensate accordingly. We invite all applicants to share their salary expectations, and we are fully prepared to tailor a package that reflects your unique clinical experience and value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Centria Offers:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clinical Quality First&lt;/strong&gt; – We prioritize outcomes, not billables. Our proprietary &lt;em&gt;CareConnect&lt;/em&gt; platform streamlines everything from treatment planning to data collection so you can stay focused on care, not paperwork.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assent-Based Care at Scale&lt;/strong&gt; – Lead meaningful change through our commitment to assent, practical functional assessment, and skills-based treatment, built into every part of our model.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real Work-Life Balance&lt;/strong&gt; – Predictable caseloads, manageable schedules, and dedicated support teams mean no last-minute chaos and no burnout.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You&#39;re Never Alone&lt;/strong&gt; – With layered support from Clinical Directors, Area Clinical Directors, and our Clinical Excellence Team, you&#39;ll always have someone in your corner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No Operational Headaches&lt;/strong&gt; – We handle the logistics. From scheduling to onboarding of technicians, our operations team keeps everything running smoothly behind the scenes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Career Growth on Your Terms&lt;/strong&gt; – Whether you&#39;re driven to lead your own Center/Academy, or apply your skills in a new department, we’re committed to supporting your growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We Invest in You&lt;/strong&gt; – From CEU stipends and paid CEU days to exclusive internal training events, we’re serious about keeping you sharp—and helping you level up.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Perks That Actually Matter&lt;/strong&gt; – Annual, all-inclusive vacation for two, early wage access, a company car or mileage reimbursement, and full benefits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No Non-Compete&lt;/strong&gt; – We don’t believe in holding people back. We believe in supporting your professional agency, even if that takes you on a path outside of Centria in the future.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Role &amp;amp; Impact as an Associate Director of Clinical Services:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Associate Director of Clinical Services will also assist in maintaining an efficient supervision structur

